Package com.danielly.jsf.cinema.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Hall
    The class Hall holds the information about a hall, the number of seats and the layout.
    Movie
    The class Movie holds the information about a movie such as the name of the movie, director etc.
    Order
    The class Order holds the information about an order such as the total price and credit card information.
    Price
    The class Price holds the information about the price of ticket based on the category.
    Seat
    The class Seat holds the information about the seat, its hall and its position in the layout of the hall.
    Showtime
    The class Showtime holds the information about the Showtime, the time, the movie, the hall and the price.
    ShowtimeSeat
    The class ShowtimeSeat holds the information about the seats of a showtime.
    Ticket
    The class Ticket holds the information about the ticket.
    TicketSeat
    The class TicketSeat holds the information about the seats of the tickets.
    User
    The class User holds the information about the user.
